{"tid":831358,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Linux 之父為過往暴躁壞脾氣道歉，並退出社群運作學習待人處事之道","createTime":"2018-09-22T01:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T06:00:16.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03663952e870ec22829e7a2e9fd074e370e4791e","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:31:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/09/18/linux-founder-apologize-for-his-bad-temp-and-step-down-from-community-for-learning-how-to-work-with-people/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2Flinux-founder-apologize-for-his-bad-temp-and-step-down-from-community-for-learning-how-to-work-with-people%2F&d=btRH%2BgKU%2F93JxdNHxl2m7DM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=ba3feba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/09/18/linux-founder-apologize-for-his-bad-temp-and-step-down-from-community-for-learning-how-to-work-with-people/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/05145339/linus-torvalds-lc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F05145339%2Flinus-torvalds-lc3.jpg&h=235053cc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nLinus Torvalds 是 Linux 作業系統的創辦人，並且主持多年的社群工作，從中還發展出影響相當大的分散式版本控制系統 Git。但 Torvalds 的壞脾氣，卻是遠近皆知，常成為媒體報導焦點。如今 Torvalds 良心發現，為他過往不好脾氣道歉，並宣布暫時從 Linux 社群運作退下來。"},{"pid":"6bf874cc443b18df5425a53d464a488bd0bc203e","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"Torvalds 趁 Linux 4.19-rc4 釋出的公告，宣布向過往他爆粗口的對象抱歉。並且會從社群工作退出，好好休養並且在離開的這段時間修身養性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lore.kernel.org/lkml/CA+55aFy+Hv9O5citAawS+mVZO+ywCKd9NQ2wxUmGsz9ZJzqgJQ@mail.gmail.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flore.kernel.org%2Flkml%2FCA%2B55aFy%2BHv9O5citAawS%2BmVZO%2BywCKd9NQ2wxUmGsz9ZJzqgJQ%40mail.gmail.com%2F&d=btRH%2BgKU%2F93JxdNHxl2m7DM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=025bdc45\" target=\"_blank\">https://lore.kernel.org/lkml/CA+55aFy+Hv9O5citAawS+mVZO+ywCKd9NQ2wxUmGsz9ZJzqgJQ@mail.gmail.com/</a>"},{"pid":"d76ee7a8d0a97e029b048c893529efd3d5825b9b","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:32:05.000Z","msg":"Torvalds 表示，他會萌生退出的想法，源自於他最近忘了 Linux Kernel Maintainers&rsquo; Summit 的時間，安排家族旅行。最後要大家配合他的行程在愛丁堡辦半天的邀請制會議，再補助大家在溫哥華活動的門票。<br />\n<br />\n另外 Torvalds 還心生想要不參加 Kernal Summit 的想法，而他已經參加二十多年了。他覺得他有愧對社群的想法，也許該暫時退出。"},{"pid":"6ee597c5ae3d84d54cc108fbe5f647dca42e3515","tid":831358,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"我都反省自己點同其他人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75447c2d4884c0e04941b9be3090a05fc40ebd21","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"對於像發明 Linux 作業系統，如 Torvalds 這樣的聰明人來說，常常不能理解一般人的想法，而有不適當的舉動和發言。像是先前 Torvalds 曾罵 Intel Meltdown 的修補是垃圾，以及 2015 年因為 Nvidia 對 Linux 支援不佳的問題，而對 Nvidia 爆粗口。<br />\n<br />\n從 Linux 社群的大人物 Torvalds 的爭議言行，可以看到<span style=\"color: red;\">開源社群常常被人詬病，常瀰漫有毒害的社群氣氛。這也是技術之外，開源社群要維繫人的參與，除了活躍的貢獻之外，還必須有健康的討論風氣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59734f9404c402fac97c89d0b3eff974bb4c1879","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"A 生都要好好學習下"},{"pid":"e3165dc4a116f2df1ac1413bcf6fdb23f9cb19e8","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:39:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/125961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F125961&d=btRH%2BgKU%2F93JxdNHxl2m7DM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=511f11dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/125961</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Linux之父道歉後，Linux社群頒佈開發人員行為準則</span></span><br />\n<br />\n這個《行為準則》是依據《貢獻者公約》（Contributor Covenant）為基礎制訂而成，Linux核心開發人員Kroah-Hartman指出，希望從此以後，Linux社群遵循這套規範來建立一個，可以讓更多人樂於參與的環境。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s4.itho.me/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/linuxkai_fa_zhe_zhun_ze_.jpg?itok=k0RpTvSy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.itho.me%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Flinuxkai_fa_zhe_zhun_ze_.jpg%3Fitok%3Dk0RpTvSy&h=0358db77&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n本周Linux之父Linus Torvalds 出人意表地發表懺悔錄後，Linux社群周二再公佈關於開發人員的言行的行為準備，不過社群反應不一。<br />\n<br />\n近日因為Torvalds搞錯時間，迫使一場Linux核心開發人員重要會議必須改期，引發社群對Torvalds長久以來態度不佳的不滿終於爆發。本周Torvalds對被他言語傷害甚至從社群中趕走的開發人員公開致歉。他還表示要休息一段時間深自檢討，學習理解他人情緒並適當回應。<br />\n<br />\n開發人員為理念爭鋒相對是司空見慣的行為，難免造成不快。事實上，過去Linux是有一套衝突準則（Code of Conflict）來規範大家的言行，但顯然效果不彰。於是Linux社群決定頒佈行為準則（Code of Conduct）。Linux核心開發人員Greg Kroah-Hartman指出，衝突準則並未達促進文明及「be excellent to each other」的精神的隱含目的。從Linux 其他專案及其他領域來看，使用明示的準則效果卓著。<br />\n<br />\n《行為準則》是依據《貢獻者公約》（Contributor Covenant）為基礎制訂而成。Kroah-Hartman指出，從此以後，Linux社群應遵循這些規範以便讓核心社群成為大家都樂於參與的環境。<br />\n<br />\n這項宣言也獲得多位Linux核心成員，包括Chris Mason、Dan Williams、Jonathan Corbet 、Olof Johansson、Steven Rostedt及Torvalds本人的簽署。"},{"pid":"dd235bcdb967e0e42977056159aa35585c73cbd5","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:42:11.000Z","msg":"《貢獻者公約》的宗旨指出，「為促進開放而自由的環境，Linux頁獻者及維護者誓將協助專案及社群所有人都能免於騷擾，不論年齡、體形、身障、種族、性別特徵、性別認同和表徵、經驗深淺、教育程度、社經地位、國際、外表、宗教或性向等。」<br />\n<br />\n這份公約鼓勵使用正向的行為，包括包容性言語、尊重不同觀點及經驗、有建設性的批評、以社群利益優先、對其他成員展現同理性。而使用性別化的語言和圖像及有色眼光、大聲、污辱／貶抑的發言、個人或政治攻擊、公開或私下騷擾、未經明顯同意公佈他人隱私資訊如住家地址或電郵、以及在專業場合中一切不適切的行為都是不可接受的。<br />\n<br />\n公約並指出，Linux專案維護者有責任釐清行為標準，並在遇到不可接受行為時做出適當且公平的矯正。如果專案貢獻者有不適切、威脅性、冒犯性及傷害性的行為時，維護者有權利及責任刪除、編輯或拒絕相關的評論、wiki edit或程式碼，或是暫時甚至永久停止貢獻者的權限。"},{"pid":"efc7c1d01f6f0e6c34da5cfcfe43429f8ec2e2de","tid":831358,"uid":4525,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"59734f9404c402fac97c89d0b3eff974bb4c1879","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"A 生都要好好學習下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"so sweet"},{"pid":"1c157ad17af021ebe693f05d275a1e652b5411b8","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc7c1d01f6f0e6c34da5cfcfe43429f8ec2e2de","tid":831358,"uid":4525,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"59734f9404c402fac97c89d0b3eff974bb4c1879","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"A 生都要好好學習下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"so sweet"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b2c6e327ab9da76401c7c6aea6a6af6a379f0b","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b2312ed1d969774fc4f6d0fa545947a533a510","tid":831358,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"因為自己失敗話 linux 難用既人應該要反省下"},{"pid":"8ca41c461bc36a417fe544617af556e8610d1b69","tid":831358,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d0b2312ed1d969774fc4f6d0fa545947a533a510","tid":831358,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"因為自己失敗話 linux 難用既人應該要反省下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T